data.description: Nice home in Culeoka subdivision.  Come make this your home so you can enjoy the front porch or back deck in this nice fall weather. Home has a vaulted ceiling and a wood burning fireplace.  This house has been well taken care of, new HVAC system installed in 2015. New hot water heater in 2019.  The sink & disposal has been replaced.  Roof was replaced in 2006.  New flooring in living area in 2010, new flooring in the large primary bedroom in 2017.  Lots of potential to make this your dream home. Nice book shelves in living area.  Storage/ office/play area in half of the garage. Make it a special area for you!
